sophia) rather than the possession of it.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Mrz 2024) 0aLovevEarly works to 1800. 0aLovexEarly works to 1800. 4aLiterature : Literary History. 4aPhilosophy : Ancient Greek Philosophy. 4aPhilosophy : Plato. 7aPHILOSOPHY / History & Surveys / Ancient & Classical.2bisacsh1 aWelton, William A., eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013z978311148737340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978079147766340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780791477663423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780791477663/original  a978-3-11-148737-3  SUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles